    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great in the driveway! It\u2019s clean, well-loved, and ready to hit the road for its next chapter. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and see it for yourself!",
