    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal traction out of corners. The vehicle exhibits sharp turn-in thanks to its balanced 50/50 weight distribution and MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry. Maintenance is up to date with the critical VANOS system serviced and a subframe reinforcement already performed. While it shows the honest patina of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, its mechanical integrity remains robust, offering the linear power delivery and visceral induction note synonymous with BMW M\u2019s golden era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
