      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes a perfect balance between performance and practicality, presenting in beautiful condition. The exterior maintains a deep, reflective finish with only minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free; the seats show minimal wear, and all electronic features\u2014including the navigation system and climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car has been fastidiously maintained, featuring a complete service history that translates to a smooth, quiet, and responsive driving experience. It is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter, offering the premium feel of a high-end model at a sensible price point.",
