    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great parked in the driveway! It\u2019s had some fun adventures and definitely has plenty of life left for its next owner. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s been well-cared for without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
