      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the S54B32 high-revving inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with essential rear subframe reinforcement plates, ensuring structural integrity under high torque loads. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing the original MacPherson strut/multi-link configuration for superior lateral grip. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and cooling system refresh. A true driver's car with the mechanical pedigree to match its legacy.",
